      "text": "Un pawehleju jums tanni Laikâ/ un fazziju: Tas KUNGS juhfu Deewirr jumscho Semmi par Jhpaschumu dewis/ wif-fi tad/ kas stipri Wihri irr/ eita apbrunnotti juhfu Brahtu to Israëka Behrnu Preekschâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bes ween juhfas See-was/ un juhfis Behrnizus un juhfit gannamu Pulku/(jo es sin-mn/ ka jums leels gannams Pulks irr) laid tas paleek juhfdês Piissahtdês/ fo es jums dewis esmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teekans tas KUNGS juhseim Brahteem Duffschanu dohs/ ittin ka jums/ ka tee arrid-san eemanto to Semmi/ fo tas KUNGS juhfu Deevs winneem dohs/ winnpufs Jardanas/ tad buhs jums atgreestees ikweenam us fawn Jhpaschunu/fo es jums dewis esmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es pawehleju arridsan Josuium tanni Laikâ/ un fazziju: Tavas Azxis irr redsejschas wifs-fu/fo tas KUNGS juhfu Deevs Scheem diwt Rehnixeem darrijs irr/ ta darrihs tas KUNGS wiffahin Walstibahm us kurren tu eefi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne bihstreetes par teem/ jo tas KUNGS juhfu Deews karrohs preefsch jums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es luhsfu arridsan to KUNGutanni Laikâ/ un fazziju:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kungs/KUNGS/tu effi eefahzis tavam Kalpam parah-diht tavu Augstibu/ un tavu stipru Rohku/ jo kur irr tahds STIPRAJS DEEWS Debbesi un wirs Semmes/ kas darriht warretu pehz tavveem Darbeem/un pehz tavu Spehku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Laid es luhssans pahreemu/ raundsians to labbu Semmi/ kas winnpufs Jardanas irr/ tohs jaukus Kalnus un to Lihbanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS ap-dufinojahs juhsu deht prett mañ/ un ne paklausija mann/ bet tas KUNGS fazzija us man: Laid tas tew gann irr/ ne runna wairs us man no schihs Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uskahp us Pisgas Gallu/ un pazell tavas Azxis prett Wahtaru/ un prett Seemeli/un prett Deenas-Widdu/ un prett Rihteem/ un pahrubko to ar ta-wahin Azzin/ jo tew ne buhs pahr scho Jardanu eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pawehl tad Josuium/ un apstiprini winnu/ un eedrohschi-ni winnu/ jo winch pahrees scho Lauschu Preekschâ/ un dohs win-neein par Jhpaschunu to Sem-mi/ fo tu redseji.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tud palikkam mehs tanni Eelejâ prett Bet-Peoru.\n"
    }
  ],
